node.title: Person dies in late night crash in Northland
node.description: A person has died following a single-car crash near Mangawhai, Northland.
node.content:
["A person has died following a single-car crash near Mangawhai, Northland.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "Emergency services were alerted to the crash on Devich Rd at around 11.35pm last night.", "The road was closed for a period as contractors repaired power lines that had come down but was reopened at about 5am today, police say.", "Enquiries into the circumstances of the crash are continuing."]
